    "texte_orig": "You[SP]changed[SP]your[SP]mind?[SP]That's[SP]too[SP]bad.\nOur[SP]offer's[SP]still[SP]on[SP]the[SP]table[SP]if[SP]you[SP]have\nthe[SP]money,[SP]though.",
